Package tile

Class Tile

java.lang.Object
tile.Tile
public class Tile extends Object
The class responsible for the attributes of a Tile. There are 3 kinds of Tiles: Path, Tunnel and Grass. Each one of them has different properties and image (selected theme also affects it).
